file_content.text: Fa'athra's palace. Same Hutt style, a lot more firepower. Ready to go in when you are.
There it is. The belly of the beast. It doesn't look like we're going to have to break in, but the place is crawling with Fa'athra's cronies.
Gotta love the music, gotta love the smells. We survive all this, you owe me a drink.
Nem'ro really is full of surprises. I mean, for an underhanded, gluttonous, backstabbing slob, who'd have thought his palace could be so... clean.
